data.description: Welcome to your new Home! This inviting 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom  and 1 Bonus Room this home offers over 912 sq ft of  living space. Featuring Tile Floors throughout.  The open layout invites you in and encourages a sense of family togetherness. These Appliances and Cabinets make your Kitchen look cleaner and Brighter. It has an outside laundry room along with a roofed utility room with doors.THIS PROPERTY DOES NOT HAVE HOA ( Homeowner Associations). Leaving Through the kitchen you have access to the oversized fully fenced back yard that is perfect for entertaining year round. This property is located in the heart of Bartow which puts you just moments away from all the conveniences including shopping, restaurants, schools, county offices, Hwy 98 and Hwy 60 – everything you need to make life easier! Schedule your private showing today and don’t miss out on this amazing opportunity to own a piece of Florida paradise. Buyer agent must verify the measurements of the rooms.: Submit all offers with Approval Letter or Proof of funds.
